---
/** Section 1 — Why NEVARA exists. Copy status: DRAFT. */
---

<section id="why" class="section-pad" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="label-caps kicker">Why NEVARA exists</p>
        <h2 id="why-heading" class="font-display why-headline">
          Restoration is happening.<br />
          <em>Proof is not.</em>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="why-body reveal" data-reveal-delay="120">
        <p>
          Across the world, organisations are reviving lakes, rebuilding forests and restoring
          wetlands. The work is real. But when a funder, a government body or an auditor asks
          what actually changed, the answer is too often scattered photographs and memory.
        </p>
        <p>
          NEVARA exists to close that gap. We convert satellite observation into verified
          environmental evidence — so that patient, decades-long ecological work can be seen,
          trusted and defended.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <figure class="why-figure reveal" data-reveal-delay="200">
      <img
        src="/assets/sequence/desktop/frame_0160.webp"
        alt="Aerial view of lakes, rivers and forest with monitored site boundaries traced across the landscape"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1406"
        height="698"
      />
      <figcaption class="label-caps">Monitored restoration sites · satellite observation</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .kicker {
    color: var(--color-moss);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 96px);
    align-items: end;
  }

  .why-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, var(--text-section));
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .why-headline em {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-forest);
  }

  .why-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    color: rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.75);
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  .why-figure {
    margin-top: clamp(48px, 7vw, 96px);
  }
  .why-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  }
  .why-figure figcaption {
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }
</style>
